7656be5dd9a143ece23a5e5bd5df9fff0495d64d14eb22426795346caec4cd330d5a5c2940792f5c8e5409ba953be6a2d41e3d6f542101f4a85ac3ea06c5c9de  unbundle-snappy.patch
4a7c7c152fa02a3daf0a0ced57dce02999a5758ccb4217d4ed53c8bbafcfb21453212c93464f646b0f7e6579b4e9cc7afb50b7fcfafbce6e0f647b9ea234e5d5  fix-depends.patch"
